high_descs: Turn around and walk to the end of the sink and turn left.
Pick up the apple from the sink.
Lift the apple above the counter.
Place the apple on the counter to the right of the sink.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle from the sink
Cut the apple with the knife.
Put the knife down on the counter to the right of the apple.
Pick up an apple wedge from the counter.
Turn left and go to the microwave.
Put the apple into the microwave, turn it on, and then remove the apple.
Turn back toward the counter with the apple.
Place the apple on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Cut an apple and put it in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right and step forward to face the sink.
Pick up the apple in the sink.
Look up to face the counter to the right of the sink.
Place the apple on the counter to the right of the sink.
Pick up the knife in the sink.
Cut the apple on the counter into three pieces.
Place the knife to the right of the apple on the counter.
Pick up the piece of apple on the sink.
Take a step to the left to face the microwave.
Heat the piece of apple in the microwave and remove it.
Turn right to face the counter to the right of the sink.
Place the piece of apple on the counter.
anns.task_desc: To heat a piece of apple and place it to the right of the sink.

high_descs: Turn around, go forward, turn left at the sink
Pick up the apple from the sink
Move a bit to the left
Put the apple on the counter
Pick up the knife from the sink
Cut the apple on the counter
Put the knife on the counter
Pick up an apple piece from the counter
Turn left and go to the microwave
Put the apple piece in the microwave, start the microwave, wait, pick up the apple piece from the microwave
Turn around, go forward a bit, turn left
Put the apple piece to the counter
anns.task_desc: Cut an apple, cook a piece of apple
